data.title: Memphis Grizzlies Roster
data.meta_description: Memphis Grizzlies scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
Jaren Jackson, Jr. was selected as the #4 pick in the First Round of the 2018 NBA Draft by the Memphis Grizzlies. Jaren Jackson, Jr. signed a multi-year contract with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 1, 2018.

Ja Morant was selected as the #2 pick in the First Round of the 2019 NBA Draft by the Memphis Grizzlies. Ja Morant signed a multi-year contract with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 1, 2019.

Draft Rights to Dillon Brooks, the #15 pick in the Second Round of the 2017 NBA Draft, were acquired by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Houston Rockets on June 22, 2017. Dillon Brooks signed a multi-year contract with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 21, 2017. Dillon Brooks signed a multi-year extension with the Memphis Grizzlies on February 5, 2020.

Draft Rights to Brandon Clarke, the #21 pick in the First Round of the 2019 NBA Draft, were acquired by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 6, 2019. Brandon Clarke signed a multi-year contract with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 7, 2019.

Grayson Allen was acquired in a trade by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Utah Jazz on July 6, 2019.

Gorgui Dieng was acquired in a trade by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Minnesota Timberwolves on February 6, 2020.

Josh Jackson was acquired in a trade by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Phoenix Suns on July 7, 2019.

De'Anthony Melton was acquired in a trade by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Phoenix Suns on July 7, 2019.

Jonas Valanciunas was acquired in a trade by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Toronto Raptors on February 7, 2019. Jonas Valanciunas re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 11, 2019.

Justise Winslow was acquired in a trade by the Memphis Grizzlies from the Miami Heat on February 6, 2020.

Kyle Anderson signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 8, 2018.

Marko Guduric signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 31, 2019.

Tyus Jones signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Memphis Grizzlies on July 9, 2019.

Jontay Porter signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Memphis Grizzlies on March 8, 2020.

Anthony Tolliver signed a contract with the Memphis Grizzlies on March 2, 2020. Anthony Tolliver re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Memphis Grizzlies on June 23, 2020.
